OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRemaining
OL,6,Fovercast and rather mild with mist and
OL,7,Fareas of fog becoming more extensive
OL,8,Fovernight. Many places staying dry,
OL,9,Falthough some isolated light rain or
OL,10,Fdrizzle is possible at times.
OL,11,
OL,12,CMonday:FExtensive low cloud and any
OL,13,Fdrizzle slowly lifting, with brighter
OL,14,Fspells possible during the afternoon.
OL,15,FMainly dry, although isolated showers
OL,16,Fpossible from late afternoon. Feeling
OL,17,Fmilder, especially in any sunshine.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
