OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:
OL,6,FBreezier Tuesday, with bright spells
OL,7,Fpossible ahead of overnight rain.
OL,8,FWednesday, morning rain clearing, then
OL,9,Fbrighter with isolated, blustery
OL,10,Fshowers following. Windier on
OL,11,FThursday, perhaps with some rain.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
